OL,3,CBody found in canal in Wolverhampton
OL,5,FA cordon was in place at a stretch of
OL,6,Fthe canal in Wolverhampton after a
OL,7,Fbody was found.
OL,9,FPolice were called to reports of a
OL,10,Fman's body in the canal off Broad
OL,11,FLane, Wednesfield, just after 7am on
OL,12,FSaturday.
OL,14,FIt was around the canal towpath
OL,15,Fbetween Lichfield Road and Broad Lane
OL,16,FNorth.
OL,18,FOfficers were seen around the entrance
OL,19,Fgate of the towpath and a cordon was
OL,20,Fin place.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/3
