OL,3,CBody found in canal in Wolverhampton
OL,5,FA spokesperson for West Midlands
OL,6,FPolice said: "We were called to
OL,7,Freports of a man's body in a canal off
OL,8,FBroad Lane, Wednesfield at just after
OL,9,F7am today (Saturday, 21 March).
OL,11,F"Sadly he was confirmed dead at the
OL,12,Fscene and we are working to identify
OL,13,Fhim and inform next of kin.
OL,15,F"His death is currently being treated
OL,16,Fas non-suspicious."
